Work for as long as you feel  in the Flow!
Your next rest duration will be adapted 
accordingly.
Set work/rest ratio to your liking.

____________

Traditional Pomodoro included!
Get notified when you need a break.

___________

Using Toggl to track your work?
Flow Timer has build-in integration
for saving time entries.

___________

Be Save - Flow Timer doesn't collect
or transfer ANY of your data, period.

If you're using Toggl integration, your 
api key is saved in your browser ONLY.